/* Two salts, two saturation routes, ONE package:
     - KCl                 -> the eNRTL electrolyte model (ion-activity Ksp; antisolvent).
     - potassiumBitartrate -> its own solubility CURVE c_sat(T) (no ion params needed).
   The activityModel slot selects eNRTL; the crystalliser that targets KHT falls back to
   its curve automatically (useElec is per-solute).  Self-contained: components + ion/tau
   catalogue under constant/. */
components       ( water ethanol KCl potassiumBitartrate );
activityModel    { model eNRTL; }
equationOfState  { model idealGas; }
